						 <p>I dunno, I feel like we have a lot of anomalous boats and this one doesn't stand out. Cherenkov radiation is something we need to move away from as far as &quot;real-life special effects&quot; goes, it's been done to death. The &quot;god child&quot; thing didn't really interest me, and the appearance of a rival vessel, while clever, wasn't enough to save the whole article in my opinion. Just, not feeling this one, sorry.</p> 
